1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,770
=Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,770 --> 00:00:40,520
=Episode 9=

3
00:00:42,833 --> 00:00:43,916
The Northern Bureau matter is settled.

4
00:00:44,291 --> 00:00:45,666
You asked Mr. Ye for help?

5
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:48,000
He loves the wine at Chong'er Pavilion.

6
00:00:48,125 --> 00:00:49,833
Getting his help was easy.

7
00:00:50,291 --> 00:00:50,916
Chang Beiming.

8
00:00:51,375 --> 00:00:52,458
Who exactly are you?

9
00:00:53,666 --> 00:00:54,791
I am

10
00:00:55,291 --> 00:00:56,708
a friend you can trust.

11
00:00:57,416 --> 00:00:58,500
If we are friends,

12
00:00:58,875 --> 00:01:00,166
why not tell me the truth?

13
00:01:00,708 --> 00:01:02,208
When have I not told you the truth?

14
00:01:02,416 --> 00:01:04,250
Everyone knows Young Master Chang
of Chong'er Pavilion.

15
00:01:05,833 --> 00:01:06,208
Fine.

16
00:01:07,333 --> 00:01:08,416
Since you will not tell the truth,

17
00:01:08,916 --> 00:01:09,875
I will stop asking.

18
00:01:10,291 --> 00:01:11,166
I would hate to be annoying.

19
00:01:11,166 --> 00:01:11,833
Then

20
00:01:12,541 --> 00:01:13,833
let me ask you something.

21
00:01:15,583 --> 00:01:16,083
What?

22
00:01:17,583 --> 00:01:18,541
What is it

23
00:01:19,083 --> 00:01:19,875
that you wear inside your clothes?

24
00:01:23,333 --> 00:01:23,875
This...

25
00:01:23,875 --> 00:01:24,375
See?

26
00:01:25,041 --> 00:01:26,833
You are not honest with me either.

27
00:01:27,083 --> 00:01:29,000
So why push me so hard?

28
00:01:33,541 --> 00:01:34,000
Fine.

29
00:01:34,833 --> 00:01:35,666
I will tell you.

30
00:01:38,666 --> 00:01:39,041
Go on.

31
00:01:42,416 --> 00:01:43,458
Five years ago,

32
00:01:44,041 --> 00:01:44,916
on my master's orders,

33
00:01:45,166 --> 00:01:46,083
I was hunting

34
00:01:46,083 --> 00:01:47,958
the Iron-Blooded Three Eagles,
ranked No. 21 on the Bounty List.

35
00:01:50,166 --> 00:01:51,583
It was my first mission.

36
00:01:51,666 --> 00:01:52,666
To complete it well,

37
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,750
I chased the Iron-Blooded
Three Eagles nonstop

38
00:01:54,750 --> 00:01:55,541
for three days and nights.

39
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,166
At last, those three outlaws

40
00:01:58,458 --> 00:01:59,333
were forced into a corner.

41
00:01:59,958 --> 00:02:00,416
(Take her down!)

42
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,875
Their poisoned darts were not deadly,

43
00:02:15,583 --> 00:02:17,500
but they left the victim weak
and paralyzed,

44
00:02:17,791 --> 00:02:18,500
unable to fight.

45
00:02:19,041 --> 00:02:20,125
I had lost all hope.

46
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,833
Then someone suddenly appeared.

47
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,041
With one move,
they killed all three men

48
00:02:25,458 --> 00:02:26,083
and saved me.

49
00:02:31,916 --> 00:02:33,583
They carried me into a hollow tree.

50
00:02:34,208 --> 00:02:35,291
I was burning with fever,

51
00:02:36,041 --> 00:02:36,916
and they cared for me all night.

52
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,750
They saved me.

53
00:03:05,708 --> 00:03:07,083
But I was poisoned and unconscious,

54
00:03:08,041 --> 00:03:09,416
so I never saw their face.

55
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:49,350
(A Humble Gift)

56
00:03:55,916 --> 00:03:57,541
(May I know which master saved me?)

57
00:03:58,125 --> 00:03:59,083
(May we meet?)

58
00:03:59,083 --> 00:04:00,333
(I wish to thank you in person.)

59
00:04:37,625 --> 00:04:39,291
That is how I got this amulet.

60
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:43,833
That story

61
00:04:44,916 --> 00:04:45,750
is rather touching.

62
00:04:46,166 --> 00:04:47,500
What was that laugh?

63
00:04:48,125 --> 00:04:49,208
Do you think I am lying?

64
00:04:49,583 --> 00:04:50,416
No.

65
00:04:51,458 --> 00:04:54,541
I just think the story

66
00:04:54,541 --> 00:04:56,708
is a little dramatic.

67
00:04:56,708 --> 00:04:57,708
What makes you say that?

68
00:04:57,916 --> 00:05:00,791
Think about it.
This master must have been a god.

69
00:05:00,791 --> 00:05:02,250
One strike, three men down.

70
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:02,958
Bang, bang.

71
00:05:03,291 --> 00:05:03,750
Besides,

72
00:05:03,958 --> 00:05:05,333
all great masters these days

73
00:05:05,333 --> 00:05:06,416
help people without asking for thanks.

74
00:05:06,625 --> 00:05:08,375
They come and go as they please.
So very dashing.

75
00:05:09,208 --> 00:05:10,166
Didn't you say

76
00:05:11,250 --> 00:05:12,541
you don't like men?

77
00:05:13,083 --> 00:05:15,083
Was your savior a man or a woman?

78
00:05:16,583 --> 00:05:17,291
How would I know?

79
00:05:18,041 --> 00:05:19,250
I was too grateful to think about that.

80
00:05:19,625 --> 00:05:20,875
I never wondered if it was a man
or a woman.

81
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:22,875
And,

82
00:05:23,541 --> 00:05:24,916
my savior

83
00:05:25,541 --> 00:05:27,125
was probably about my father's age.

84
00:05:29,125 --> 00:05:30,791
When they cared for me,

85
00:05:31,291 --> 00:05:33,375
it felt like when I was sick as a child,

86
00:05:33,916 --> 00:05:35,541
and my father looked after me.

87
00:05:36,541 --> 00:05:37,833
I'm seriously starting to doubt

88
00:05:37,833 --> 00:05:39,375
whether this story is true at all.

89
00:05:40,291 --> 00:05:42,125
Maybe the poison took effect,

90
00:05:42,541 --> 00:05:43,416
and you hallucinated.

91
00:05:43,625 --> 00:05:44,541
Then who killed the Three Eagles?

92
00:05:44,541 --> 00:05:45,708
How would I know?

93
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:47,916
Even if this master really existed,

94
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,041
they

95
00:05:49,916 --> 00:05:50,916
may not be a good person.

96
00:05:51,208 --> 00:05:52,875
Do not speak that way of my savior.

97
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:54,791
I told you my secret.

98
00:05:55,125 --> 00:05:56,375
Now you must tell me one of yours.

99
00:05:58,708 --> 00:05:59,541
Fine.

100
00:06:00,250 --> 00:06:01,041
I will tell you.

101
00:06:08,458 --> 00:06:09,916
My secret is...

102
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:14,500
I am allergic to pineapple.

103
00:06:15,208 --> 00:06:15,958
Chang Beiming!

104
00:06:16,458 --> 00:06:17,250
You are awful.

105
00:06:18,125 --> 00:06:19,666
It is a secret.

106
00:06:19,916 --> 00:06:20,833
I never promised

107
00:06:20,833 --> 00:06:22,083
to tell you who I really am.

108
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:24,041
Men really are all liars.

109
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,416
I will never believe you again.

110
00:06:28,125 --> 00:06:28,916
Bingfan.

111
00:06:28,916 --> 00:06:30,666
Don't bring me pineapple next time.

112
00:07:22,166 --> 00:07:23,500
(Now that I know the truth,)

113
00:07:24,375 --> 00:07:26,250
(why do I still feel uneasy?)

114
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,291
Go, go.

115
00:07:36,666 --> 00:07:37,291
Bingfan.

116
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,166
Constable Guan is here.

117
00:07:43,041 --> 00:07:45,291
Guan Yunfeng, Eighth-Rank Head Constable
of the Enforcement Division,

118
00:07:45,791 --> 00:07:46,416
at your service.

119
00:07:47,375 --> 00:07:48,791
Constable Guan, please sit.

120
00:07:53,083 --> 00:07:53,791
Why is the Jinyiwei here?

121
00:07:55,041 --> 00:07:56,375
Miss, may I

122
00:07:56,916 --> 00:07:58,208
ask your name?

123
00:07:58,916 --> 00:08:01,083
Constable Guan,
do you have news of Diaotu?

124
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:02,958
Constable Guan?

125
00:08:04,416 --> 00:08:05,125
Since that day,

126
00:08:06,083 --> 00:08:07,500
he has not appeared again.

127
00:08:11,208 --> 00:08:13,500
Did your men search
near Marquis Taiping's manor?

128
00:08:13,875 --> 00:08:15,500
My men searched every street

129
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:16,083
near Marquis Taiping's manor.

130
00:08:16,375 --> 00:08:17,416
There was no sign of him.

131
00:08:18,375 --> 00:08:19,166
That predator

132
00:08:19,666 --> 00:08:20,916
seems to have vanished into thin air.

133
00:08:24,500 --> 00:08:26,416
The deadline to catch him
is almost up.

134
00:08:27,625 --> 00:08:29,208
How will we answer our superiors?

135
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:31,291
Bingfan,

136
00:08:31,541 --> 00:08:33,458
why don't we discuss this with Hua?

137
00:08:35,125 --> 00:08:35,791
Excuse me.

138
00:08:38,916 --> 00:08:39,375
Miss.

139
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:42,250
What is it?

140
00:08:42,791 --> 00:08:44,500
I still don't know your name.

141
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:49,416
Shen Bingfan, Squad Leader
of the Jinyiwei Northern Bureau.

142
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:57,666
Shen Bingfan.

143
00:09:00,958 --> 00:09:01,625
What a lovely name.

144
00:09:03,180 --> 00:09:05,390
(Northern Bureau)

145
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,458
My lord.

146
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:10,250
Today is the last day
of the ten-day deadline.

147
00:09:10,541 --> 00:09:11,958
If you must explain this to the Cabinet,

148
00:09:12,208 --> 00:09:13,083
please take us with you.

149
00:09:14,291 --> 00:09:15,000
For what?

150
00:09:15,291 --> 00:09:16,583
So we can all get scolded together?

151
00:09:16,875 --> 00:09:17,291
Enough.

152
00:09:17,625 --> 00:09:19,583
I will handle this matter.

153
00:09:20,125 --> 00:09:21,166
You trusted us,

154
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:22,583
but we failed at the start.

155
00:09:25,166 --> 00:09:27,375
How is that a failure?

156
00:09:27,625 --> 00:09:29,583
At least you scared that scum enough

157
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,791
to keep him from showing himself.

158
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,625
That still counts as

159
00:09:32,791 --> 00:09:34,291
protecting security around the capital.

160
00:09:34,875 --> 00:09:35,500
Doesn't it?

161
00:09:35,875 --> 00:09:36,250
All right.

162
00:09:36,625 --> 00:09:37,791
Don't feel pressured.

163
00:09:38,083 --> 00:09:39,166
Don't carry this burden.

164
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:41,833
I will bear it alone.

165
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,416
My lord.

166
00:09:43,208 --> 00:09:45,375
Diaotu is very likely hiding
in the Marquis's manor.

167
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:47,791
With your permission,
I will investigate again.

168
00:09:47,791 --> 00:09:49,750
No, no. Don't go.

169
00:09:50,458 --> 00:09:52,375
I value caution above all.

170
00:09:52,583 --> 00:09:53,333
The case is still unsolved.

171
00:09:53,333 --> 00:09:55,250
Do not cause an even bigger mess.

172
00:09:58,666 --> 00:10:00,666
My lord, Young Master Chang said

173
00:10:00,916 --> 00:10:01,666
that because of us,

174
00:10:02,125 --> 00:10:03,500
you were reprimanded by the Cabinet

175
00:10:03,958 --> 00:10:05,791
and mocked by Mr. Duan
of the Southern Bureau.

176
00:10:07,208 --> 00:10:07,708
It is nothing.

177
00:10:08,625 --> 00:10:09,625
I'm old and thick-skinned.

178
00:10:10,083 --> 00:10:11,541
So they chewed me out a little.

179
00:10:12,625 --> 00:10:13,416
No big deal.

180
00:10:15,875 --> 00:10:16,875
I don't care.

181
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:18,833
My lord.

182
00:10:19,833 --> 00:10:22,041
I don't recall
having much connection with you.

183
00:10:22,291 --> 00:10:23,416
Why do you protect me like this?

184
00:10:30,458 --> 00:10:31,583
You are the daughter of my old friend.

185
00:10:37,416 --> 00:10:38,583
Of course I would protect you.

186
00:10:40,041 --> 00:10:41,083
You know who I am?

187
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:45,208
Your father was Jinyiwei
Qianhu Shen Lian, wasn't he?

188
00:10:46,125 --> 00:10:47,125
The first time you came here,

189
00:10:48,333 --> 00:10:49,791
I already knew who you were.

190
00:10:52,791 --> 00:10:53,416
Get up.

191
00:10:56,875 --> 00:10:59,416
How did you get so bold?

192
00:11:00,041 --> 00:11:02,958
How dare you sneak into my Bureau
as a female Jinyiwei?

193
00:11:04,083 --> 00:11:04,791
Such obsession.

194
00:11:05,333 --> 00:11:06,375
So deep.

195
00:11:07,416 --> 00:11:08,750
You came for revenge, didn't you?

196
00:11:09,833 --> 00:11:12,541
Commander, please help me
uncover the truth

197
00:11:12,791 --> 00:11:13,625
and clear my father's name.

198
00:11:15,625 --> 00:11:17,000
If I knew the truth,

199
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:19,958
I would have cleared your father's name
long ago.

200
00:11:20,333 --> 00:11:22,708
You wouldn't have had
to come here yourself.

201
00:11:24,208 --> 00:11:25,541
You don't know the truth either?

202
00:11:27,791 --> 00:11:30,000
I only know part of what happened.

203
00:11:31,083 --> 00:11:32,125
Please tell me, my lord.

204
00:11:32,583 --> 00:11:33,416
I know

205
00:11:33,416 --> 00:11:34,666
that the men sent to receive your father

206
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,500
were Lu Guokai, then a Jinyiwei Qianhu,

207
00:11:38,125 --> 00:11:40,500
and Wang Yan, then Commissioner

208
00:11:41,166 --> 00:11:43,291
of the Southern Bureau, now Commander

209
00:11:44,125 --> 00:11:44,583
of the Five Armies Command.

210
00:11:45,083 --> 00:11:46,208
Wang Yan

211
00:11:46,416 --> 00:11:48,500
is also a direct subordinate

212
00:11:49,166 --> 00:11:49,791
of the current Southern Bureau
Commander.

213
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:52,041
Lu Guokai?

214
00:11:52,708 --> 00:11:54,500
Lu Guokai was sent to receive my father?

215
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:56,875
According to Lu Guokai's report,

216
00:11:57,083 --> 00:11:58,958
when he and Wang Yan arrived,

217
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:02,166
the witness and your father
had already been killed.

218
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:05,708
Prince Luo's case

219
00:12:06,125 --> 00:12:07,083
involved too many people.

220
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:09,958
The court didn't want
a greater scandal exposed,

221
00:12:10,375 --> 00:12:12,541
so it handled the case quietly.

222
00:12:13,666 --> 00:12:14,458
That means

223
00:12:15,541 --> 00:12:17,916
it was Lu Guokai or Wang Yan
who framed my father.

224
00:12:17,916 --> 00:12:18,375
Bingfan!

225
00:12:24,708 --> 00:12:25,458
Remember this.

226
00:12:26,125 --> 00:12:28,375
Without solid proof,

227
00:12:28,791 --> 00:12:30,500
never suspect your colleagues.

228
00:12:31,916 --> 00:12:32,500
Yes, my lord.

229
00:12:33,250 --> 00:12:35,791
Lu Guokai is greedy and self-serving,

230
00:12:36,375 --> 00:12:37,791
but he doesn't have the nerve.

231
00:12:38,125 --> 00:12:40,208
Wang Yan is reckless and bold,

232
00:12:40,625 --> 00:12:43,458
but he is nothing more than a brute
with courage but no brains.

233
00:12:43,958 --> 00:12:44,500
He

234
00:12:46,458 --> 00:12:47,625
doesn't have the mind for it.

235
00:12:49,416 --> 00:12:50,166
My lord,

236
00:12:50,375 --> 00:12:52,291
please help me uncover the truth
of what happened.

237
00:12:54,666 --> 00:12:55,500
This case

238
00:12:56,791 --> 00:12:57,875
has been buried for too long.

239
00:12:58,791 --> 00:13:01,333
I can't help you rashly.

240
00:13:03,541 --> 00:13:04,083
However,

241
00:13:04,666 --> 00:13:06,125
if it is about investigating Leng Xin,

242
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:08,541
I can offer you a few leads.

243
00:13:10,125 --> 00:13:11,125
If we can capture Leng Xin,

244
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:12,916
the truth will naturally come to light.

245
00:13:13,625 --> 00:13:14,500
Please tell me, my lord.

246
00:13:17,333 --> 00:13:17,833
Bingfan,

247
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:21,041
let me tell you a secret.

248
00:13:21,791 --> 00:13:23,500
Since Leng Xin first appeared,

249
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:26,375
he has had no equal
in the martial world.

250
00:13:26,833 --> 00:13:27,583
The only one

251
00:13:27,583 --> 00:13:30,416
he truly fears is the phantom thief
Feng Fuliu.

252
00:13:32,291 --> 00:13:34,500
If you can find Feng Fuliu,

253
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:37,375
you will find a way to counter Leng Xin.

254
00:13:41,708 --> 00:13:42,500
What is it?

255
00:13:43,333 --> 00:13:44,250
(On the night of the full moon.)

256
00:13:44,625 --> 00:13:46,083
(To the venerable Duke Wei.)

257
00:13:46,625 --> 00:13:47,958
(I shall take the imperial-bestowed
Azure Dragon Jade.)

258
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:49,291
(Feng Fuliu.)

259
00:13:49,291 --> 00:13:49,750
Bad news!

260
00:13:50,541 --> 00:13:52,166
The phantom thief Feng Fuliu
has sent a calling card.

261
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:00,958
Hua. Miss Shen. Miss Cheng.

262
00:14:01,583 --> 00:14:02,583
I heard that last night,

263
00:14:02,583 --> 00:14:04,208
the phantom thief Feng Fuliu
appeared in the capital.

264
00:14:04,958 --> 00:14:08,458
They say he sent a challenge letter

265
00:14:08,583 --> 00:14:09,458
to Duke Wei's manor.

266
00:14:10,041 --> 00:14:12,166
He said that on the night
of the full moon,

267
00:14:12,291 --> 00:14:14,625
he will steal Duke Wei's
imperial-bestowed Azure Dragon Jade.

268
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:15,458
Today,

269
00:14:15,833 --> 00:14:17,583
Duke Wei reported it to the court.

270
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:19,666
Now the Three Judicial Offices,

271
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:20,916
the Southern and Northern Bureaus,

272
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:23,041
and the Five Armies Command
are all in an uproar.

273
00:14:25,291 --> 00:14:26,541
Feng Fuliu has appeared.

274
00:14:28,166 --> 00:14:29,916
The imperial-bestowed
Azure Dragon Jade...

275
00:14:31,416 --> 00:14:32,541
It must be worth a fortune.

276
00:14:33,333 --> 00:14:34,416
The Commander

277
00:14:34,750 --> 00:14:35,958
has been summoned
to the Cabinet to discuss it.

278
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,916
It seems Feng Fuliu

279
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:41,500
is really going to throw the capital
into chaos.

280
00:14:43,041 --> 00:14:43,875
Good chance.

281
00:14:47,208 --> 00:14:47,875
What did you say?

282
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,500
Say that again?

283
00:14:50,833 --> 00:14:52,583
I request permission
to arrest Feng Fuliu.

284
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,416
Shen Bingfan.

285
00:14:55,583 --> 00:14:56,708
Who do you think you are?

286
00:14:56,958 --> 00:14:57,250
I...

287
00:14:57,250 --> 00:14:59,500
Even if we send Jinyiwei officers,
it won't be you female Jinyiwei.

288
00:15:00,250 --> 00:15:01,458
You failed to capture Diaotu last time.

289
00:15:01,583 --> 00:15:03,000
Do you know how much shame
that brought on the Jinyiwei?

290
00:15:03,458 --> 00:15:04,208
Go, go.

291
00:15:04,208 --> 00:15:04,500
Out.

292
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:05,333
Get out.

293
00:15:07,250 --> 00:15:09,333
We failed to catch Diaotu last time.

294
00:15:09,666 --> 00:15:11,208
That was embarrassing.

295
00:15:11,875 --> 00:15:14,875
But if we catch Feng Fuliu this time,

296
00:15:15,708 --> 00:15:17,666
wouldn't that be worth
far more than catching Diaotu?

297
00:15:17,958 --> 00:15:18,375
By then,

298
00:15:18,375 --> 00:15:21,041
we female Jinyiwei will win back
all our dignity.

299
00:15:22,291 --> 00:15:23,041
Hua is right.

300
00:15:23,708 --> 00:15:25,083
But the Cabinet has assigned

301
00:15:25,375 --> 00:15:26,583
Feng Fuliu's case
to the Ministry of Justice.

302
00:15:27,041 --> 00:15:29,791
The Commander and Commissioner Lu
both warned us repeatedly

303
00:15:30,125 --> 00:15:31,333
not to act rashly.

304
00:15:31,583 --> 00:15:32,833
Are you silly?

305
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:35,500
If we go as private citizens

306
00:15:35,833 --> 00:15:38,125
and manage to catch Feng Fuliu,

307
00:15:39,291 --> 00:15:42,833
the credit will naturally go
to the Northern Bureau.

308
00:15:43,875 --> 00:15:45,583
And if we do not catch him,

309
00:15:46,208 --> 00:15:47,708
we can say we were just passing by.

310
00:15:48,083 --> 00:15:49,333
They cannot really blame us for that.

311
00:15:49,333 --> 00:15:49,791
Bingfan.

312
00:15:50,875 --> 00:15:53,166
You two are both trying
to convince me today.

313
00:15:53,666 --> 00:15:54,458
That is strange.

314
00:15:56,833 --> 00:15:58,125
To be honest,

315
00:15:58,583 --> 00:16:01,208
we are very curious about Feng Fuliu.

316
00:16:01,708 --> 00:16:03,000
Aren't you curious?

317
00:16:04,125 --> 00:16:05,708
Of course I want to catch him too.

318
00:16:06,208 --> 00:16:07,083
Then it is settled.

319
00:16:09,041 --> 00:16:10,375
Then we

320
00:16:11,208 --> 00:16:13,500
will lie in wait outside
Duke Wei's manor

321
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,625
on the night of the full moon.

322
00:16:16,083 --> 00:16:18,166
If we can catch Feng Fuliu,

323
00:16:19,875 --> 00:16:22,666
let us see who still dares to say
female Jinyiwei are useless.

324
00:16:24,916 --> 00:16:25,416
Fine.

325
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:30,470
(Treasure Pavilion)

326
00:16:35,625 --> 00:16:36,458
Anything unusual?

327
00:16:36,708 --> 00:16:37,083
No.

328
00:16:37,125 --> 00:16:37,416
No.

329
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:39,270
(Treasure Pavilion)

330
00:16:44,458 --> 00:16:45,041
Watch out!

331
00:17:12,125 --> 00:17:13,250
Much obliged, Constable Guan.

332
00:17:14,958 --> 00:17:16,125
This Azure Dragon Jade

333
00:17:17,291 --> 00:17:18,500
shall be mine to admire for a few days.

334
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,333
Ladies, enjoying the evening?

335
00:17:23,125 --> 00:17:23,625
Feng Fuliu.

336
00:17:24,375 --> 00:17:25,041
Ladies,

337
00:17:26,541 --> 00:17:27,500
until we meet again.

338
00:17:29,625 --> 00:17:30,291
You are not getting away!

339
00:17:38,375 --> 00:17:39,791
You used the Three Wildcat Leaps.

340
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:41,375
Who are you?

341
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,666
Your figure is familiar too.

342
00:17:43,958 --> 00:17:44,958
Who are you?

343
00:17:45,666 --> 00:17:48,208
The spring wind dares
to brush the willows.

344
00:17:48,791 --> 00:17:51,458
The night rain comes unseen
to nourish the flowers.

345
00:18:02,666 --> 00:18:03,166
Hua.

346
00:18:05,708 --> 00:18:06,166
Duoyu.

347
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:06,916
Hua.

348
00:18:06,916 --> 00:18:08,416
My eyes hurt so much.

349
00:18:09,541 --> 00:18:10,041
Hua.

350
00:18:10,458 --> 00:18:11,750
Let me check your injury.

351
00:18:12,083 --> 00:18:13,375
No need.

352
00:18:14,416 --> 00:18:14,958
Hua.

353
00:18:16,333 --> 00:18:17,250
How are you? Are you all right?

354
00:18:17,541 --> 00:18:19,666
I'm sorry. Feng Fuliu got away.

355
00:18:20,041 --> 00:18:21,166
Did you see his face clearly?

356
00:18:21,666 --> 00:18:22,333
I...

357
00:18:22,375 --> 00:18:24,208
I don't think I saw it clearly.

358
00:18:24,833 --> 00:18:26,416
But his silhouette

359
00:18:26,541 --> 00:18:29,666
felt like someone we all know very well.

360
00:18:29,875 --> 00:18:31,000
Chang Beiming.

361
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:50,190
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

362
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:53,940
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

363
00:18:54,190 --> 00:18:57,190
♪My heart drifted lost♪

364
00:18:57,190 --> 00:19:00,600
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

365
00:19:01,690 --> 00:19:04,900
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

366
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:08,650
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

367
00:19:09,230 --> 00:19:11,440
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

368
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:15,480
♪I've softly let it go♪

369
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:19,350
♪The vow you made was true♪

370
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:23,100
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

371
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:25,310
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

372
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:29,850
♪And forget at world's end♪

373
00:19:30,150 --> 00:19:31,650
♪Embracing memory♪

374
00:19:31,650 --> 00:19:34,020
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

375
00:19:34,020 --> 00:19:37,900
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

376
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:40,230
♪I wish to let it pass♪

377
00:19:40,230 --> 00:19:45,230
♪And run toward this vast life♪

